"title": "8208: commitment, to God",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8208",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Commitment to God arises from faith in his promises, is expressed in worship and adoration and leads to obedience to his commands.</p>\n<h2>Commitment to God commanded</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut27:10\">DEU 27:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:14\">JOS 24:14</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom12:1-Rom12:2\">ROM 12:1–12:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:13\">DEU 6:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12-Deut10:13\">DEU 10:12–10:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut13:4\">DEU 13:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:5\">JOS 22:5</a> <em>Joshua reiterates Moses' commands</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg6:10\">JDG 6:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam7:3\">1SA 7:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:24\">1SA 12:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:9\">1CH 28:9</a> <em>David's instructions to Solomon</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr19:9\">2CH 19:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:20\">JER 38:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess4:1\">1TH 4:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:22\">2TI 2:22</a></p>\n<h2>Obedience to God's commands as a sign of commitment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut7:9\">DEU 7:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh24:24\">JOS 24:24</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:17\">ROM 6:17</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:8\">EXO 19:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:22\">DEU 11:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs8:61\">1KI 8:61</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh10:29\">NEH 10:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:6-Ps40:8\">PSA 40:6–40:8</a> <em>The reference may be to the ear-piercing that was a sign of slaves' voluntary commitment to their masters</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer7:23\">JER 7:23</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer11:3\">JER 11:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer38:20\">JER 38:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer42:6\">JER 42:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hag1:12\">HAG 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech6:15\">ZEC 6:15</a>JHN <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech14:15\">14:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:10\">JHN 15:10</a>\n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts5:29\">ACT 5:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:13\">ROM 2:13</a></p>\n<h2>Love for God and worship of him are hallmarks of commitment</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:6\">DEU 30:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John21:15\">JHN 21:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12\">DEU 10:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:1\">DEU 11:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:13\">DEU 11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:22\">DEU 11:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:11\">JOS 23:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh1:5\">NEH 1:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa56:6-Isa56:7\">ISA 56:6–56:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer20:12\">JER 20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan9:4\">DAN 9:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:24\">MAT 6:24</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:13\">LUK 16:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37\">MAT 22:37</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:30\">MRK 12:30</a></p>\n<h2>Benefits of commitment to God</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:20\">DEU 30:20</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr16:9\">2CH 16:9</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov16:3\">PRO 16:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:10\">REV 2:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod19:5-Exod19:6\">EXO 19:5–19:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:6\">EXO 20:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:1\">DEU 28:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:14\">1SA 12:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:2-1Kgs2:4\">1KI 2:2–2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps97:10\">PSA 97:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov2:7-Prov2:8\">PRO 2:7–2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa1:19\">ISA 1:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer26:13\">JER 26:13</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of commitment to God</h2>\n<p>Abraham:\n <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen22:17-Gen22:18\">GEN 22:17–22:18</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:8\">HEB 11:8</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num12:7\">NUM 12:7</a> <em>Moses</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:2\">JOS 22:2</a> <em>the tribes who settled in Transjordan</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:5\">1KI 15:5</a> <em>David</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:14\">1KI 15:14</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr15:17\">2CH 15:17</a> <em>Asa</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs20:3\">2KI 20:3</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr31:20\">2CH 31:20</a>; \n<a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:25\">2KI 23:25</a> <em>Josiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh13:14\">NEH 13:14</a> <em>Nehemiah</em>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:37\">JHN 13:37</a> <em>Simon Peter's good intentions</em></p>\n<h2>God's commitment of gifts and tasks to his people</h2>\n<h3>God's commitment of gifts</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor9:17\">1CO 9:17</a></p>\n<h3>God's commitment of the faith to believers</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:3\">JUD 1:3</a></p>",
